description: Goh`s Cinderace is the evolved form of Goh`s Raboot. It evolved during a battle against Oleana`s Milotic. Oleana`s Milotic was sent out to battle against Goh at the Hammerlocke Stadium to stop Goh from interfering. Milotic was defeated by Goh`s Cinderace after it evolved during the battle and learned Pyro Ball.
name: Aceburn (Gou)
